section.t:
A Diameter server MUST be configured as follows to execute realm-based redirection:
configured with an application that incorporates realm-based redirection;
the Local Action field of the routing table described in Section 2.7 of is set to LOCAL;
an application-specific field is set to indicate that the required local action is to perform realm-based redirection;
an associated application-specific field is configured with the identities of one or more realms to which the request should be redirected.
